<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f2f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #6c5ce7;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #2d3436;
        }

        .otp-box {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            color: #6c5ce7;
            background-color: #efedfd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px dashed #a29bfe;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f9f9fb;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #636e72;
        }

        .welcome-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #4834d4;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Community!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="welcome-text">Hi <%= name %>,</h2>
            <p>We're excited to have you on board. To get started and keep your account secure, please use the following
                One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your email:</p>

            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>

            <p>This code is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore
                this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Addis Ababa, Ethiopia</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>